				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$${\text{BrO}}_{3}^{ - }$$\end{document} and defluorinating PFOA in the absence of oxygen. Degradation of these oxidized compounds is probably the result of reaction with reducing radicals (eaq-\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
