				\begin{document}$${\text{e}}_{\text{aq}}^{ - }$$\end{document} and H) that are produced during water radiolysis. The more complex behavior of PFOAs indicates that other radicals such as ·OH and ·CO3-\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
